to clear up a couple of misunderstandings:<br>
<br>
1. xfers get instatagged upon arrival, and receive full loot rights upon arrival. In addition, we spend a considerable amount of guild time regearing xfers.<br>
<br>
2. officers in TCR are the ones that get -least- loot.<br>
<br>
3. ex-IV trashtalkers, just ignore them, they don't know how to keep a normal conversation going, and it seems they are spending their free time flaming around on message boards.<br>
<br>
4. My main character xfered to KB and TCR on april 1st of this year. Feel free to check my magelo for the result so far on a 89% attendance character.<br>
<br>
5. (EDIT, sorry, missed a question) We don't go dkp cause it would screw over the transfers bigtime who'd be naked for.. well.. ever. And besides, it's raining loot on KB since there's really about zero competition for mobs, so loot is never an issue in guild. What you don't get today, you'll get tomorrow or the day after. Noone cares.<br>
